reviewText: This isn't the worst horror movie I've ever seen.  It's one of the worst movies I've seen of any genre.  Bad audio,  weak story,  bad acting,  bad directing.  You name it.
I'd like to get my money back. I was tricked with the amazing dvd art. I didn't realize there was pos inside
Liked it so much I bough copies to give to friends for their Halloween movie watching! I feel like this will soon become a part of everyone's scary movie play list.
